<SYNC Start=5072424><P Class=KR>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5073160><P Class=KR>
전가요 아님 하나님인가요?
<SYNC Start=5076653><P Class=KR>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5085440><P Class=KR>
